SELECT *
FROM `blips-prod-v2.analise_de_credito.motor_analise_credito_n8n`
WHERE
  cnpjCliente = "{{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.CNPJ }}"
ORDER BY PARSE_DATETIME('%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S', dataProcessamento) DESC
LIMIT 1;

SELECT
    *
  FROM
    `blips-bigdata.RECEITA_FEDERAL.empresas`
  WHERE
    cnpj_basico = SUBSTR("{{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json['CNPJ'] }}", 1, 8)
LIMIT 1;

WITH latest_data AS (
  SELECT
    cnpj_basico,
    cnpj_ordem,
    cnpj_dv,
    cnae_fiscal_principal,
    cnae_fiscal_secundaria,
    data_situacao_cadastral,
    situacao_cadastral,
    email_contribuinte,
    ddd1,
    telefone1,
    RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY cnpj_basico, cnpj_ordem, cnpj_dv ORDER BY data_situacao_cadastral DESC) AS rank_data
  FROM
    `blips-bigdata.RECEITA_FEDERAL.estabelecimentos`
  WHERE
    cnpj_basico = SUBSTR("{{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json['CNPJ'] }}", 1, 8)
    AND cnpj_ordem = SUBSTR("{{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json['CNPJ'] }}", 9, 4)
    AND cnpj_dv = CAST(SUBSTR("{{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json['CNPJ'] }}", 13, 2) AS INT64)
)
SELECT *
FROM latest_data
WHERE rank_data = 1
LIMIT 10;
